site_name: Clare House, 10 Hawthorn Avenue, London and Playground on Hawthorn Avenue, London, E3
description: Demolition of the existing building and all structures on site and construction of two part four/part five storey buildings and a 23 storey tower providing 145 new residential dwellings (Class C3) and community floorspace (Class F2), the provision of disabled car parking spaces, cycle parking, refuse storage, mechanical plant and associated hard and soft landscaping, including upgrade works to the existing playground on Hawthorn Avenue.
